### SampleApp API - Admin User Management Endpoints
### VSCode REST Client Extension: https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=humao.rest-client
### Uses variables from backend/.env (configured in .vscode/settings.json)
### Requires: Admin authentication

@contentType = application/json

### Get token from auth.rest login endpoint first
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### Sample user ID (update with actual UUID)
@userId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000


### ===== USER MANAGEMENT =====

### List All Users
GET {{$dotenv API_URL}}/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List Users with Pagination
GET {{$dotenv API_URL}}/api/admin/users?skip=0&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get User by ID
GET {{$dotenv API_URL}}/api/admin/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update User
# Note: Admins cannot modify their own account
PATCH {{$dotenv API_URL}}/api/admin/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "first_name": "Updated",
    "last_name": "Name",
    "phone": "+1234567890",
    "company_name": "New Company"
}

### Activate User
PATCH {{$dotenv API_URL}}/api/admin/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "is_active": true
}

### Deactivate User
PATCH {{$dotenv API_URL}}/api/admin/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "is_active": false
}
